articles.title: Donald Trump Swears He’s Not a Fan of ‘Highly Overrated’ Bruce Springsteen - rollingstone.com
articles.description: After Bruce Springsteen called him 'incompetent' at his European tour opener, Donald Trump insisted he 'never liked' the musician or his music.
